Amensable -  open to suggestion or the one who follows the advice or suggestion given to him
Tharunn is very amensable about his character

persuade - instructing someone to do something through reasoning or argument
Tharunn persuaded his teacher to change the mistake in the question

commensurate -  giving or regarding them with the work the have done or something rewardable which depends on the some work he does
Software developers in google get commensurate their salary with the level of their competitive coding knowledge
